        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="min-h-screen flex flex-col justify-center items-center sm:px-8 md:px-16 lg:px-24">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-6">About Me</h1>
      <p class="text-lg mb-6">
        I'm a Software Engineer, Computer Science graduate from Nanyang Technological University, Singapore.
        Passionate in <Emp>building impactful software products</Emp> and <Emp>imparting knowledge</Emp> to others.
      </p>
